Package: safesink
Title: Safe and Numerically Stable Sinkhorn Optimal Transport
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Richard", "Martin", email = "Richard.Martin@gov.bc.ca", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: 
    Provides a numerically stable implementation of the entropy-regularized 
    optimal transport (Sinkhorn) algorithm with utilities for diagnostics,
    solver comparison, and validation.
